
DATE: NETWORKING CONCEPTS
NEED FOR NETWORKING:
 RESOURCE SHARING
 RELIABILITY
 REDUCED COST
 FAST COMMUNICATION
TYPES OF NETWORK:
LOCAL AREA NETWORK (LAN)
WIDE AREA NETWORK (WAN)
METROPOLITAN AREA NETWORK (MAN)
 A domain name is your website name.
